The paper proposes an algorithm for automatic localization and labeling of vertebra in 3D medical images using deep learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of message passing and sparsity regularization, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL) research. Finally, the paper focuses on medical imaging and diagnosis, which suggests that it could also belong to the medical imaging (cs.MED) sub-category.
